Introduction

Seokhee is a South Korean singer. He is a member of the boy group Celest1a and a former member of the boy group Kairos.

In 2022, Seokhee was a contestant on the survival shows Stars Awakening, but was sadly eliminated. He was also a contestant on MBC's survival show Fantasy Boys in 2023 but was eliminated in episode 11. In September 2024, he was revealed as a contestant on JTBC's survival show PROJECT7 starting in October 2024. He was eliminated from the show in episode 8 after ranking 38th place.
